    <item>
      <title>科伦坡证券交易所主席谈斯里兰卡总统选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-23/colombo-stock-exchange-chairman-on-sri-lanka-s-election-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科伦坡证券交易所主席迪尔尚·维拉塞卡拉 (Dilshan Wirasekara) 讨论了总统选举结果，他希望新总统能够与现有的 IMF 计划大体保持一致。他在“彭博亚洲市场”节目中与哈斯琳达·阿明 (Haslinda Amin) 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-23/colombo-stock-exchange-chairman-on-sri-lanka-s-election-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 07:02:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行行长哈萨克斯坦表示服务价格上涨比经济增长放缓更令人担忧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/ecb-s-kazaks-says-services-prices-bigger-worry-than-slow-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员马丁斯·卡扎克斯表示，目前服务业通胀持续的危险超过了他对经济的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-23/ecb-s-kazaks-says-services-prices-bigger-worry-than-slow-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 23 Sep 2024 06:48:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
